【单选题】
Analyze the following code.
#include <iostream>
using namespace std;
int m(int num) {
  return num;
}
void m(int num) {
  cout << num;
}
int main( ) {
  cout << m(2);
  return 0;
}

A、
The program has a compile error because the two functions m have the same signature.

B、
The program has a compile error because the second m function is defined, but not invoked in the main function.

C、
The program runs and prints 2 once.

D、
The program runs and prints 2 twice.

正确答案： A 我的答案：A得分： 1.4分
答案解析：

函数 m 被重载，但是它们不满足重载条件（因为形参个数和对应的类型完全一样）

